  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You deflect attacks that could mean your ally's death.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Shield Proficiency.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Whenever an adjacent ally is the target of an attack, you can, as an immediate action, grant that adjacent ally a +2 shield bonus to AC. You must be wielding a light shield, heavy shield, or tower shield to use this feat.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you use this feat, you can spend 2 stamina points to increase the shield bonus granted to your ally by an amount equal to the enhancement bonus of the shield you are using.",
